Requirements:
    1. Node version > v18:
        https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager

Setup:
    1. Clone this project:
        `git clone git@github.com:nemanja99lazic/Smile_BI_Task.git`
    2. Position in the project root directory
    3. Run the following command to install all needed dependencies:
        `npm install`

Script execution:
    1. Position in the project root directory
    2. Run the following command to run the script:
        `npm run start`

Output data:
    The output data will be written in a JSON file with the path './scraped_data/data.json'.
    The structure of the document is:
        {
            "1": {
                "price": "<price>",
                "shop_name": "<shop_name>",
                "position": 1
            },
            "2": {
                "price": "<price>",
                "shop_name": "<shop_name>",
                "position": 2
            },
            ...
        }
        
